welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Sebastian, known for its charming small-town feel and beautiful beaches. We hope you enjoy your stay and take the time to explore all that our city has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Melbourne International Airport houses all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: Terminal 1 is used for domestic flights and is home to various airlines such as Delta, American Airlines, and JetBlue.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: Terminal 2 is used for international flights and is home to airlines such as Air Canada, British Airways, and Lufthansa.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at St Lucie County Airport offers all necessary amenities for travelers, including check-in counters, security checkpoints, and a variety of dining and shopping options.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at St Lucie County Airport caters to private and charter flights, providing a more exclusive and personalized experience for travelers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.
